text: You're serious, what are you looking at?
Sorry, I was looking at something unrelated to work.

Huh, no, it's fine.
Since we're on standby, it's okay.

I was just curious because you seemed really focused.
Was there something catching your eye?

No, I was just thinking...
I just really like the atmosphere of this outfit right now...

If I ever have the chance to wear something like this
in my personal life, I think it would be nice...

I see.
It's something you might need for celebratory occasions...!

Yeah, although I wouldn't wear it very often...!
So, I'm just "thinking" about it...!
